core and Level Up, in turn allowing you to enhance abilities such as Beam Strength, Weapon Cooldown, Beam Range, Health, Missiles, Grenades and more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Larank is in it, and is known for not quite taking these sort of situations all that seriously</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tSecret areas to find, cameras to smash (after being told not to), unlockable bios and lore</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• More than 10 bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•\tFeaturing over 61 tracks by  EPIC BLARGMAN</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Over 90 unfortunately in-joke titled Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882390/extras/1f09a1bef3f8a0c9d666a99e7c4ea12f.poster.avif?t=1738071060\" width=486 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882390/extras/1f09a1bef3f8a0c9d666a99e7c4ea12f.webm?t=1738071060\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/882390/extras/1f09a1bef3f8a0c9d666a99e7c4ea12f.mp4?t=1738071060\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
